children.title: HEATING SYSTEM REBATES + EPI
children.content:
<div class="question-content-result result-epi">
    <h3 class="character-style-2 question-header">Free Energy Efficient Products and Installation</h3>
    <p class="character-style-1">1
        At absolutely no cost to you, one of our qualified Efficiency
        Partners will install energy efficient products in your home.
        Whether you rent the space or own, we can help you save. Not
        only is the installation free, but so are the products we
        install — which is when the savings really begin. With your
        newly installed energy efficient products, like LED lighting and
        faucet aerators, you can save up to $240 a year
    </p>
    <button class="btn-question">Book an Installation</button>
</div>
<div class="question-content-result result-instant-saving">
    <h3 class="character-style-2 question-header">Instant Savings</h3>
    <p class="character-style-1">
        We partner with participating retailers across the province to
        offer instant in-store rebates on dozens of energy efficient
        products for your home. Rebates are available year-round, but
        include even more products during our spring and fall campaigns.
    </p>
    <button class="btn-question">Find Rebates Near You</button>
</div>
<div class="question-content-result result-appliance-retirement">
    <p class="character-style-1 question-header">
        <svg width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 25 25" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
            <rect width="25" height="25" fill="url(#refrigerator-icon)"></rect>
            <defs>
                <pattern id="refrigerator-icon" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
                    <use xlink:href="#image0_4108_2754" transform="scale(0.01)"></use>
                </pattern>
                <image id="image0_4108_2754" width="100" height="100"
                       xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"></image>
            </defs>
        </svg>
        Do you also have a 10+ year old working fridge & freezer?
    </p>
    <button class="btn-question btn-question-secondary">
        Get $50 with Appliance Retirement
    </button>
</div>
